{"tid":1712561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想 塞 鐵 的 人 入 一 入 黎！","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T23:25:23.000Z","uid":64702,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a360f91c65f6a98218446da4a275fab2d381e9d2","tid":1712561,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:44:39.000Z","msg":"新加坡地鐵和禁令的實施<br />\n1987年，耗資50億新元建造的新加坡地鐵投入使用。這在當時是新加坡實行的最大公共項目。後來據報道，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一些破壞者把吃剩的口香糖粘在地鐵車門的傳感器上，使車門無法正常運作，影響到地鐵服務。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然此現象非常少見，但維護需要極高的費用，也很難抓到破壞者。1992年，剛接任新加坡總理的吳作棟決定發佈口香糖禁令。這一禁令隨《製造控制法》頒佈，此法律同時限定某些煙酒產品的銷售。[3]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E7%25B3%2596%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7Wo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=757f8846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n大家記住唔好學啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db234b926f8b351d9b060b32510a99e0465ac5bd","tid":1712561,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n（twitter 突發）美國參議員Hawley 為警察攻入中大校園出聲啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank